Returns examples of data field values

parameter_values.Rd

Returns examples of data field values

parameter_values(data_set = NULL, data_field = NULL)

Arguments

data_set

a character vector specifying the data set
data_field

a character vector specifying the data field

Value

returns a data frame with the unique data field values conatained in the first 1000 records of the full data set

Examples

parameter_values(data_set = "fimaNfipClaims", data_field = "totalBuildingInsuranceCoverage")
